txt.en: Talk to Dolenthol in Barad Orhant
Dolenthol can be found in Barad Orhant.\n\nYou should talk to Dolenthol.
'May I have a word with you?'
Moon Tower wraiths can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat the Moon Tower wraiths and sever their shackles.
'The old guards have been laid to rest, and slowly Minas Ithil is restored'
'The old guards have been laid to rest, and slowly Minas Ithil is restored. Still there is much more to do upon this Circle of Sorrow, my friend.'

'Good [placeholder], may I have a word with you? We have accomplished much upon the Circle of Wrath together. Perhaps it best if we continue our work upon this Circle of Sorrow.\n\n'I believe there is still good to be found in this corrupted city. Take for example the walking wraiths who were once guarding the Tower of the Crescent Moon in Minas Ithil. They serve darkness only because they know not their past. We should lay to rest these guards, so they can find peace. Do you agree with this plan, [placeholder]?'
Dolenthol calls for aid in purging the fell sorcery that enwreathes the Circle of Sorrow.
